1. After creating the k8s cluster, execute:

```
helm repo add ingress-nginx https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx
helm install nginx ingress-nginx/ingress-nginx --namespace ingress --create-namespace
```
2. Replace the Load Balancer IP from the deployment manifests (front + back) under `env` field with the one assigned by the cloud provider to the ingress' LB.
3. Apply the deployment manifests again.